        {
            "title": "德國經濟自2022年以來首年實現成長 受支出提振",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Destatis\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"612\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/XdIxhuHRRMpIGohIyIc_rw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYxMjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/1182519fe6ef062daafad9baa9cd0ef6\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Destatis</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 德國經濟自2022年以來首年實現成長，政府大規模支出助力該國擺脫了持續已久的工業衰退。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在連續兩年經濟萎縮後，2025年國內生產毛額成長0.2%，與接受彭博調查分析師的預測中值一致。第四季度實現了同等幅度的成長。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"612\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/IGLeU6uf6SvYYSaCmka_uQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYxMjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/fb6adeb71e15ba10ee9cc15ae8616a48\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">統計局周四表示，去年經濟成長主要由家庭消費和政府支出推動，而投資下降，且貿易構成拖累。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">近年來，歐洲最大經濟體因能源危機、關鍵投入品供應短缺以及唐納德·川普對全球貿易的衝擊而動盪不安 —— 這些因素對其工業腹地造成了尤為沉重的打擊。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-b7a3feac-b993-3130-915a-e2486b2311fa-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管外界樂觀認為總理弗里德里希·默茨斥資數億歐元加強軍事力量、升級破敗基礎設施的計畫能夠引發經濟復甦，但任何復甦能否持續仍存疑問。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對於未來幾年，經濟學家預計這些支出將推動經濟成長率超過1%。但他們強調，必須伴隨大規模支出實施改革，以進一步支撐需求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題German Economy Grows for First Year Since 2022 on Spending Boost</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Kristian Siedenburg、Joel Rinneby、Harumi Ichikura.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E8%87%AA2022%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A5%E4%BE%86%E9%A6%96%E5%B9%B4%E5%AF%A6%E7%8F%BE%E6%88%90%E9%95%B7-%E5%8F%97%E6%94%AF%E5%87%BA%E6%8F%90%E6%8C%AF-093132700.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-15 18:06:01",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "菲律賓將允許中國遊客免簽入境",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 菲律賓外交部周四表示，菲律賓將允許中國公民免簽入境，停留時間最長可達14天。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">菲律賓外交部稱，中國公民免簽入境菲律賓旅遊或商務的政策將於周五生效。該政策僅適用於經馬尼拉和宿務機場入境的遊客，且14天的停留期限不可延長。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該部門在聲明中表示，「這項符合總統關於促進貿易、投資和旅遊，以及加強菲律賓和中國人文交流的要求。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Philippines to Allow Visa-Free Entry for Chinese Visitors</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7e1e1627-af37-3a35-9288-e3ae2802e967-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8F%B2%E5%BE%8B%E8%B3%93%E5%B0%87%E5%85%81%E8%A8%B1%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%81%8A%E5%AE%A2%E5%85%8D%E7%B0%BD%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83-072426896.html",
